name: OpenAlexa Protocol
description:
OAP is run by a dedicated team of crypto experts, industry analysts, financial consultants and constantly growing community of OpenAlexa. It’s a unique idea to grow the network using the defi automated smart contract.
This, in turn, allows the idea of coming with our very own blockchain came from years of observing the patterns and framework of Ethereum.
While Ethereum has swept across the boundaries and practical usability of fiat currencies it is still not in the hands of the average consumer and to think that Ethereum can be used to make everyday transactions is still a far-fetched dream because of the volatile fees.
With OAP we plan to bridge this gap considerably and bring the current bottlenecks of using Ethereum as a payment application into a practically viable and usable smart application, through a deeply integrated network community.

description: Storj Labs provides secure distributed cloud storage that gives customers control over their data.
